This Week’s Japanese Switch Sales

29 new games have been added to the Japanese Switch eShop sales including 40% off LOVERS in a Dangerous Spacetime (¥949), 50% off The Liar Princess and the Blind Prince (¥3,769), 50% off Downwell (¥250), 20% off Katana ZERO (¥1,264), 30% off The Messenger (¥1,386), and many more. Check out the full list of Japanese Switch eShop sales here and video below…

summary: Speed runners are out there doing stuff like jumping off cliffs to kill the character and they say “oh no, whatever will I do,...
body:
Speed runners are out there doing stuff like jumping off cliffs to kill the character and they say “oh no, whatever will I do, the run is ruined” and then somehow they are at the final boss.

I don’t know at what points is intentional or a mistake.

The Video Game Art Archive is dedicated to scanning and extracting classic video game artwork at the best resolutions possible!

Support us on Patreon!
We update four times a day with new artwork from long forgotten games that have never had their art available. Looking for a specific game? Check out the Archive! You might get lucky!
